When I paste some text with CRLF endings into a TextField and click on the end of the line, cursor is placed after invisible `\r` char. When I press left arrow, it goes over that char to the actual text end. Now when I press right arrow, it skips to the next line like there wasn't any additional char. But that `\r` is still there after I click there with mouse again.

I found that it is `\r` by selecting it and pasting it into hex editor.

This only happens in Windows build, tried on web and it doesn't happen there. Don't know about the other platforms.

